# Optional MadSpin card. Rename to `madspin.dat` to activate (its mere presence
# turns on madspin=ON at launch and the pipeline uses the decayed LHE).
# Example: force tau -> l nu nu on a Z -> tautau subprocess.
# set seed 1
# set spinmode none
# decay ta+ > e+ ve vt~
# decay ta+ > mu+ vm vt~
# decay ta- > e- ve~ vt
# decay ta- > mu- vm~ vt
# launch
